00:11:51.010 --> 00:11:52.790 align:middle line:90%
Now why is that important?

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:55.420 align:middle line:84%
Because it is a
fact we have thrown

00:11:55.420 --> 00:11:59.750 align:middle line:84%
tremendous amounts of carbon
dioxide into the atmosphere.

00:11:59.750 --> 00:12:02.980 align:middle line:84%
We have now created more
of a carbon dioxide burden

00:12:02.980 --> 00:12:04.690 align:middle line:84%
in the Earth's
atmosphere than we

00:12:04.690 --> 00:12:07.480 align:middle line:84%
have in the 420,000 years
