00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:11.060 align:middle line:84%
We've never seen this much
CO2 in the atmosphere.

00:12:11.060 --> 00:12:14.800 align:middle line:84%
So if in the past,
higher levels of CO2

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:17.560 align:middle line:84%
