degree of cooling because

00:12:23.050 --> 00:12:25.300 align:middle line:90%
of the higher degrees of CO2.

00:12:25.300 --> 00:12:26.630 align:middle line:90%
Why is that important?

00:12:26.630 --> 00:12:29.950 align:middle line:84%
Well a lot of that cooling
happens north of the equator.

00:12:29.950 --> 00:12:33.910 align:middle line:84%
The bulk of the earth's landmass
is north of the equator.

00:12:33.910 --> 00:12:35.890 align:middle line:84%
The bulk of the
world's population

00:12:35.890 --> 00:12:37.230 align:middle line:90%
is north of the equator.

00:12:37.230 --> 00:12:39.620 align:middle line:84%
And most of our food is
