changes the conditions

00:12:50.260 --> 00:12:52.990 align:middle line:84%
that allow us to grow the food
and support the industries

00:12:52.990 --> 00:12:53.830 align:middle line:90%
that we depend upon.

00:12:53.830 --> 00:12:55.390 align:middle line:90%
So this is important.

00:12:55.390 --> 00:12:57.310 align:middle line:84%
And I think it is
important for us

00:12:57.310 --> 00:13:01.270 align:middle line:84%
to be honest, truthful,
and factual with ourselves.

00:13:01.270 --> 00:13:03.280 align:middle line:84%
I asked earlier in
the program how can we

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:07.090 align:middle line:84%
