00:13:07.090 --> 00:13:07.930 align:middle line:90%
about the extreme?

00:13:07.930 --> 00:13:11.870 align:middle line:84%
And this is a perfect example
of exactly what I mean here.

00:13:11.870 --> 00:13:14.770 align:middle line:84%
So the question that
obviously comes up

00:13:14.770 --> 00:13:18.790 align:middle line:84%
