00:16:56.980 --> 00:16:59.890 align:middle line:10%
And we're having a little
bump in eccentricity.

00:16:59.890 --> 00:17:02.650 align:middle line:10%
We're seeing that coincide
with the obliquity.

00:17:02.650 --> 00:17:05.410 align:middle line:84%
So we're seeing this
dance the Earth is

00:17:05.410 --> 00:17:08.319 align:middle line:84%
doing in a very precise
way that has created

00:17:08.319 --> 00:17:10.960 align:middle line:84%
warming in the past, and it's
doing the same thing right now.

00:17:10.960 --> 00:17:12.849 align:middle line:84%
I would expect to
